{
  "stem": "11611.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He did the design for the airplanes, I don't think he did anything on the engines.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Swiss were courting him, the British were courting him, I don't think the French were, but the Americans certainly were.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Americans were ready to pick up anybody in Germany that would be useful.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bear in mind that by '47, '48, the Cold War was underway and the thinking was not in terms of World War II.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was in terms of the next one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a result of which, the United States, among other countries, brought in a great number of German scientists, about half of whom had a very thorough Nazi taint.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As you well know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Swiss brought him to our billet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a cook.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We could make our meals there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a German cook.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They brought him as a dinner guest one evening, and I was sitting in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was probably, oh, I wasn't so damn old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was probably the senior member of the group in the billet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I sat to dinner with him and I quickly concluded he was a first class son of a bitch who explained to everybody assembled that of course the Germans had only killed about 100,000 Jews, and they were all criminals.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the problem and the reason why the Germans had to launch the war was because they had restricted markets, and couldn't trade much, and the rest of the world had been oppressing Germany and threw out the usual Nazi garbage to the effect that all of this was a consequence of very bad treatment in the Versailles Treaty and post-World War I.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I knew who I was dealing with.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you see fit to contradict him in that regard?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
